query:
SELECT p.id, p.nome as projeto_nome, COUNT(c.id) as total_clientes 
FROM projects p 
LEFT JOIN clientes c ON c.projectId = p.id 
GROUP BY p.id, p.nome 
ORDER BY p.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 5;
